## Option 3: Third-Party Add-ons (The "No-Code" Route)

If you don't want to manage code or GCP architecture, several reliable third-party marketplace tools specialize in this. They usually require installing a lightweight "agent" or gateway on your local network to securely tunnel the data without opening firewall ports.

* **SeekWell / Kloudio:** Great for scheduling SQL queries to dump straight into Sheets.
* **Coefficient / Supermetrics:** Highly polished user interfaces designed specifically for turning databases into live spreadsheet dashboards.

